**newly reaped fresh paddy or well soaked dried paddy is fried in a shallow earthen pot till one or two grains begin to pop it is thereafter pounded quickly in a wooden mortar till the grain is flattened**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   அவல்
-


